886
00:43:46,410 --> 00:43:47,529
in front of everyone.

887
00:43:47,530 --> 00:43:49,280
It's embarrassing.

888
00:43:56,809 --> 00:43:57,720
Master,

889
00:43:57,800 --> 00:43:58,808
